metadata.name: amplituhedron
metadata.description:
(Amplituhedron is a geometric structure that changes the concept of reality.
  It is not a physical object but an abstraction that helps scientists understand particles
  computing its volume is a geometric question whose answer presents a new definition of the concept of space-time ...)

  Complicated, boring,
  Like "her"

  This is a love story,  About "her"
  She is complicated
I'm confused
I want to understand her
But she is a "Amplituhedron"
 
Oil painting on canvas  50Ã—60 cm   2020
